{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017reLYf573Cy6uVt198hzLZ","type":"tool_result","content":"File created successfully at: /Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Oscypek Smażony.generated.21.txt"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"39fa0393-55f5-48c6-9ef5-33cf17b4d5f5","uuid":"bb55ad94-892b-47d7-9a2d-7007697977fc","tool_use_result":{"type":"create","filePath":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Oscypek Smażony.generated.21.txt","content":"Oscypek Smażony\nPan-Fried Smoked Cheese / Oscypek Grillé\n\nSKŁADNIKI (INGREDIENTS):\n- 4 oscypek (traditional smoked cheese wheels, ~100g each)\n- 2 tbsp vegetable oil\n- 2 tbsp butter\n- 4 tbsp lingonberry or cranberry preserve\n- Fresh thyme sprigs for garnish\n- Sea salt flakes\n- Cracked black pepper\n\nPRZYGOTOWANIE (PREPARATION):\n\nRemove oscypek from refrigerator 15 minutes before cooking to bring to room temperature.\nThis prevents cheese from hardening when fried.\n\nHeat oil and butter together in large skillet over medium-high heat until butter foam\nsubsides. Temperature should be just below smoking point.\n\nCarefully place oscypek wheels in pan, being gentle not to break delicate shape. Fry\n2-3 minutes per side until golden crust forms. Cheese should remain firm inside while\nexterior caramelizes slightly.\n\nTransfer to serving plates immediately. Top with generous spoonful of lingonberry preserve\nand fresh thyme sprigs. Season with sea salt and cracked pepper.\n\nSERVING SUGGESTIONS:\nServe immediately while still warm. Pairs well with crusty bread, fresh vegetables, or\ngreen salad. In Poland, often accompanied by horseradish sauce or mustard.\n\nTIPS:\nIf oscypek unavailable, can substitute halloumi cheese or fresh mozzarella, though flavor\nand texture will differ from traditional mountain cheese. Keep temperature consistent to\nachieve perfect golden exterior and creamy interior.\n\nServes 2-4 as appetizer or light main course.\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
