{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01JQ5HKBfn11wSSspHseeGWb","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01MCULGzC4yniNFnLK1XGH2u","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Karp Pieczony.generated.21.txt","content":"Karp Pieczony\nRoasted Carp with Almond & Raisin Sauce\n\nSKŁADNIKI / INGREDIENTS:\n- 1 whole carp (2-3 kg), cleaned and gutted\n- 1 large onion, sliced\n- 3 carrots, sliced into rounds\n- 2 celery stalks, chunked\n- 4 bay leaves\n- 6 peppercorns\n- 1/2 cup raisins, soaked in warm water\n- 3/4 cup roasted almonds, coarsely chopped\n- 4 tbsp butter\n- 2 tbsp flour\n- 1 cup fish or vegetable stock\n- 1 tbsp Dijon mustard\n- 2 tbsp apple cider vinegar\n- Salt and pepper to taste\n- Fresh parsley for garnish\n\nPRZYGOTOWANIE / PREPARATION:\n\nScore skin of carp diagonally at 2-inch intervals, being careful not to pierce flesh.\nThis helps seasonings penetrate and skin crisps properly.\n\nIn large roasting pan, arrange half the vegetables (onion, carrot, celery) and all bay\nleaves and peppercorns. Lay carp on vegetables, season inside cavity and outside with\nsalt and pepper.\n\nTop fish with remaining vegetables. Dot with 2 tbsp butter. Roast uncovered at 375°F\nfor 35-40 minutes until flesh flakes easily.\n\nWhile fish roasts, make sauce: melt remaining butter, whisk in flour to create roux.\nToast 1 minute, add stock slowly, stirring constantly. Add drained raisins, chopped\nalmonds, mustard, and vinegar. Simmer 5 minutes until thickened.\n\nRemove carp from oven and carefully transfer to serving platter. Strain roasting pan\njuices and add to almond sauce.\n\nPour warm sauce over fish, garnish with fresh parsley. Serve with boiled potatoes or\nrye bread to absorb delicious sauce.\n\nNOTES: Carp is traditional Christmas Eve fish in Poland. Flesh is delicate, sweet.\nServes 4-6. Sauce can be made ahead.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":608,"cache_read_input_tokens":86316,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":608},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"39fa0393-55f5-48c6-9ef5-33cf17b4d5f5","uuid":"52a2ba4b-7c03-452e-a419-bb4a620d9802"}
